---
title: Crumbed Fish Tacos with Charred Pineapple Salsa & Zesty Slaw
description: It’s the freshness of the ocean wrapped up in a taco, it can’t get any better. Oh wait, it can because we’re crumbing these dory fillets with a smokey Aussie spice mix. Bring it back to the beach with a pineapple salsa and these tacos are very hard to beat.
